      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "★ מטרה: Scale + Enterprise\n\nSprint 17-18 (חודש 9):\n• Order Routing AI\n• Advanced Inventory Forecasting\n• Batch tracking + Expiry alerts\n\nSprint 19-20 (חודש 10):\n• Custom Reports Builder\n• BI מתקדם\n• Data Export + Webhooks API\n\nSprint 21-22 (חודש 11):\n• Native Mobile למנהלים\n• Voice ordering (Whisper API)\n• Auto-substitute OOS\n\nSprint 23-24 (חודש 12):\n• Enterprise features\n• White-label option\n• Scale to 100+ tenants\n• יעד הכנסה חודשית: 100K₪+",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "★ מטרה: Scale + Enterprise\n\nSprint 17-18 (חודש 9):\n• Order Routing AI\n• Advanced Inventory Forecasting\n• Batch tracking + Expiry alerts\n\nSprint 19-20 (חודש 10):\n• Custom Reports Builder\n• BI מתקדם\n• Data Export + Webhooks API\n\nSprint 21-22 (חודש 11):\n• Native Mobile למנהלים\n• Voice ordering (Whisper API)\n• Auto-substitute OOS\n\nSprint 23-24 (חודש 12):\n• Enterprise features\n• White-label option\n• Scale to 100+ tenants\n• יעד הכנסה חודשית: 100K₪+",
